data.description: Rare find on Okaloosa Island, within a 1/4 mile to the Gulf and Sound.  With some TLC this could be a great investment property or vaction rental.  Walking distance to restaurants, stores and public beach access is right across the street.  The main level has the living room with a rock fireplace, kitchen and a half bath.  Upstairs are 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom.  The 3rd level loft has a bedroom and a half bath.  There are covered patios at the front and back of the first floor of the unit, as well as an open patio on the second floor.  Located near both Hurlburt Field and Eglin AFB.
